Invert 'if' statement quick task in editor should behave nicer, should have some optimizer for logic statements. Currently it translates this:
boolean a = true, b = false;
if(a == false && b == false) { } else { }
to
if(!a != true || !b != true) { } else { }
but it should be nicer to have simply:
if(a == true || b == true) { } else { }

